race.comment: SMART ACTION (8) has been plying his trade in harder races in town of late and will find this task much more to his liking. Maps ideally for this from gate two and should give backers a great sight. The consistent BOVIDAE (7) got the job done over this track and trip last time out and will have taken some confidence from that overdue victory. Top-three credentials with a repeat of that performance. The very well-related MARENARO (5) (half to 2xG1 winner and stallion Home Affairs) is better than recent efforts suggest and can bounce back without surprising. PREPOTENT (6) is a last-start winner that shouldn't be underestimated.
